import base64, binascii
cipher=base64.b64decode(open('magic.b64','rb').read())
png_header=b'\x89PNG\r\n\x1a\n'
assert len(png_header)==8
next_chunk=b'\x00\x00\x00\rIHDR'
portion=cipher[8:16]
print(binascii.hexlify(portion))
key2 = bytearray()
for i in range(8):
    key2.append(portion[i]^next_chunk[i])
print(key2)
```
